### Listar todos os usuários
GET https://localhost:3000/usuario
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Buscar usuário por ID
GET https://localhost:3000/
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Criar usuário comum
POST https://localhost:3000/api/usuario
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Gustavo Silva",
  "email": "gustavo@email.com",
  "senha": "senha123"
}

###

### Criar usuário administrador
POST https://localhost:3000/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Maria Admin",
  "email": "maria@email.com",
  "senha": "senha123",
  "cargo": "admin"
}

###

### Criar usuário com e-mail duplicado (deve retornar 409)
POST https://localhost:3000/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Outro Gustavo",
  "email": "gustavo@email.com",
  "senha": "senha123"
}

###

### Criar usuário com dados inválidos (deve retornar 400)
POST https://localhost:3000/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "",
  "email": "email-invalido",
  "senha": "123"
}

###

### Atualizar nome do usuário
PUT https://localhost:3000/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Gustavo Atualizado"
}

###

### Atualizar e-mail do usuário
PUT https://localhost:3000/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "gustavo.novo@email.com"
}

###

### Atualizar senha do usuário
PUT https://localhost:3000/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "senha": "novaSenha456"
}

###

### Atualizar cargo para admin
PUT https://localhost:3000/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cargo": "admin"
}

###

### Desativar usuário
PUT https://localhost:3000/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ativo": false
}

###

### Atualizar usuário inexistente (deve retornar 404)
PUT https://localhost:3000/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Fantasma"
}

###

### Remover usuário
DELETE https://localhost:3000/
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Remover usuário inexistente (deve retornar 404)
DELETE https://localhost:3000/
Content-Type: application/json
